<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Merchant Search</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }
    .merchant-search {
      width: 399px;
      height: 896px;
      background: white;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }
    .bounding-box {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      left: 25px;
      top: 50px;
      position: absolute;
      background: #D9D9D9;
    }
    .arrow-back {
      left: 4px;
      top: 4px;
      position: absolute;
    }
    .add-new-commodities {
      color: black;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      position: absolute;
      left: 25px;
      top: 80px;
    }
    .frame-188 {
      padding-left: 11px;
      padding-right: 11px;
      padding-top: 4px;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      left: 26px;
      top: 156px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 5px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      display: inline-flex;
    }
    .all {
      color: #131313;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .frame-190 {
      padding-left: 11px;
      padding-right: 11px;
      padding-top: 4px;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      left: 73px;
      top: 156px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 5px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      display: inline-flex;
    }
    .rectangle-122 {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      left: 74px;
      top: 167px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 15px;
      border: 1px #4682B4 solid;
    }
    .frame-72 {
      width: 340px;
      height: 50px;
      left: 29px;
      top: 447px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 30px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
    }
    .name-of-item {
      color: #B7B7B7;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      position: absolute;
      left: 45px;
      top: 455px;
    }
    .frame-73 {
      width: 340px;
      height: 50px;
      left: 29px;
      top: 517px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 30px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
    }
    .description {
      color: #B7B7B7;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      position: absolute;
      left: 45px;
      top: 525px;
    }
    .frame-189 {
      width: 340px;
      height: 50px;
      left: 29px;
      top: 587px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 30px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
    }
    .basic-unit-of-item {
      color: #B7B7B7;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      position: absolute;
      left: 45px;
      top: 595px;
    }
    .expand-arrow {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      left: 305px;
      top: 15px;
      position: absolute;
      background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }
    .frame-75 {
      width: 340px;
      height: 50px;
      left: 29px;
      top: 657px;
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 30px;
      outline: 1px #4682B4 solid;
      outline-offset: -1px;
    }
    .price-per-item {
      color: #B7B7B7;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      position: absolute;
      left: 45px;
      top: 665px;
    }
    .frame-115 {
      padding-left: 57px;
      padding-right: 57px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      left: 123.5px;
      top: 782px;
      position: absolute;
      background: #0B1A51;
      border-radius: 30px;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      display: inline-flex;
    }
    .save {
      color: white;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .add-image {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      left: 159px;
      top: 252px;
      position: absolute;
      background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,');
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="merchant-search">
    <div class="frame-188">
      <span class="all">All</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="bounding-box"></div>
      <div class="arrow-back">
        <svg width="16" height="17" viewBox="0 0 16 17" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M3.825 9.70996L9.425 15.31L8 16.71L0 8.70996L8 0.709961L9.425 2.10996L3.825 7.70996H16V9.70996H3.825Z" fill="#1C1B1F"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="add-new-commodities">Add New Commodities</div>
    <div class="frame-190">
      <span class="all">All</span>
    </div>
    <div class="rectangle-122"></div>
    <div class="add-image"></div>
    <div class="frame-72">
      <span class="name-of-item">Name of Item</span>
    </div>
    <div class="frame-73">
      <span class="description">Description</span>
    </div>
    <div class="frame-189">
      <span class="basic-unit-of-item">Basic Unit Of item</span>
      <div class="expand-arrow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="frame-75">
      <span class="price-per-item">Price per Item</span>
    </div>
    <div class="frame-115">
      <span class="save">Save</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
